column20: Made all - ridden after 2 out - kept on well(op 7/4 and tchd 2/1)
Prominent - went second 3 out - kept on(op 11/1 tchd 9/1 and tchd 16/1)
In touch with leaders - headway 8th - went third after 3 out - briefly went second but hung left run-in - not clear run towards finish(tchd 6/4)
Prominent - outpaced from 2 out(tchd 5/2 and tchd 3/1)
Held up in rear - not fluent 1st - some headway 3 out - weakened 2 out(op 16/1)
In touch with leaders - weakened before 2 out(tchd 66/1)
Took keen hold - raced in second - lost position after 3 out - weakened before 2 out - tailed off(op 150/1 tchd 250/1)
